text: Carola Casale (born 7 November 1998) is an Italian female karateka vice European champion at senior level at the European Karate Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Carola Casale at LesSports.info Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female karateka Category:Karateka of Fiamme Oro
